        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Hide personal info without placeholder text",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Removes the `\"Hidden\"` placeholder when `Hide personal information` is enabled, so redacted account/email fields render as empty instead.\r\n- Omits account rows that would otherwise show only an empty redacted value.\r\n- Makes LiteLLM team-budget redaction explicit by stripping team aliases before email redaction side effects can affect matching.\r\n- Adds regression coverage for normal workspace aliases and email-shaped LiteLLM team aliases.\r\n\r\n## Why\r\n\r\nUsers enabling `Hide personal information` expect private values to disappear, not be replaced with visible placeholder text. Showing `\"Hidden\"` still draws attention to where personal data exists and creates noisy UI.\r\n\r\nThe LiteLLM cleanup also makes the behavior easier to reason about and prevents future changes in email redaction formatting from accidentally changing team-budget display.\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n\r\n- `swift test --filter LiteLLMMenuCardModelTests`\r\n- `swift test --filter 'MenuCardModelTests|LiteLLMMenuCardModelTests|UsageStoreCoverageTests|CodexPresentationCharacterizationTests'`\r\n- `make check`\r\n\r\n## Screenshot\r\n\r\nBefore\r\n<img width=\"310\" height=\"56\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-25 at 09 24 37\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d9305d97-ee34-48f4-b0db-f0f77d35ab70\" />\r\n\r\nAfter\r\n<img width=\"311\" height=\"56\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-25 at 09 24 19\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/552b9280-f3da-4671-aa67-38a4166da631\" />\r\n",
